textAnnotations.description:
That it wouldn't be her fault at all. That
she was a lady who, like her Uncle Charles,
toch the highest prick in keeping her word. "/
could see Zamuder 3ting," he went on in a
lower voice, his sunker blach eyes twinklig.
3" He powerful anxious, pour Mistah Piers.
We all know how Balicon bland dangerous
to all kind of boats, wid d'ose big, big
rocks in an out o' de water.
